<div class='hero-unit'>
  <h1 class="text-center">Experience Blackjack Like You Never Have Before!</h1>
  <div id='home_picture' class="text-center">
    <img src="/images/blackjack_home.jpg" alt="blackjack picture" height="400" width="600">
  </div>
  <h3>Boasting many cutting edge features such as:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><h4>Casino-style of play</h4></li>
    <li><h4>Smart AI dealers</h4></li>
    <li><h4>Realistic graphics</h4></li>
  </ul>
  <br>
  <div class="text-center">
    <h3>You'll swear you were sitting right in a <em>real, live</em> casino!</h3>
    <a href="#nameModal" role="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" data-toggle="modal">Let's Get Started!</a>
